OL,5, Boris Johnson's ex-wife Marina Wheeler 
OL,6, KC has been appointed as Labour's      
OL,7, adviser on protecting women against    
OL,8, workplace harassment.                  
OL,10,FMs Wheeler, an employment lawyer, will 
OL,11,Flook at how to make it easier for      
OL,12,Fworkers to blow the whistle on bullying
OL,13,Fand discrimination at work.            
OL,15,FWorkplace whistleblowers are already   
OL,16,Fprotected from unfair dismissal.       
OL,18,FBut the law only applies in certain    
OL,19,Fcircumstances - such as when employers 
OL,20,Fhave committed criminal offences.      
